CustomField.description: Determines the priority of percentage availability when matching and ranking resources with Intelligent Staffing. The default value is 3. 1 is the highest priority. 2 is next highest, and so on. Priority values must be unique.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: Determines the priority of percentage availability when matching and ranking resources with Intelligent Staffing. The default value is 3. 1 is the highest priority. 2 is next highest, and so on. Priority values must be unique.
CustomField.label: Availability Priority
